description: Performs 25 mc runs at integer undersampling point in the grid of upper-width 0.15 above predicted undersampling point, with blocksoft denoiser. Sparsity varies from 0.7 to 0.95 in interval of 0.05. No. of rows varies in [3200, 6400] and no. of columns is 5. cov(resid) used to estimate the noise covariance at each iteration instead of resid.T * resid/n.
